(95, 'about_us', '<p><strong>Habiibii&nbsp;</strong>idea&nbsp;was founded in 2022 by a team of visionary entrepreneurs with a clear mission: transforming food and goods delivery into a seamless, fast, and intelligent experience for everyone. With just a few taps on the app, your order is on its way, featuring real-time tracking, ultra-fast delivery, and direct communication with the courier.<br />\r\nWe offer a wide range of services, including grocery, flower, and medicine delivery, parcel shipping, retail shopping, car rentals, on-demand services, gift purchases, freelancing, event planning, digital products, and much more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Habiibii, we provide a convenient and personalized experience, allowing customers to shop from a diverse selection of restaurants, retailers, and service providers. As a subsidiary of Muscat Green Ruins LLC, we leverage global expertise to strengthen our market position and drive innovation in the on-demand delivery industry.</p>', 'admin_landing_page', '2025-03-26 18:11:32', '2025-03-29 10:31:32'),
